or compact layouts, items can contain only icons. Padding adjusts automatically to keep the button square — no extra prop required. Always provide an `aria-label` on each icon-only item so screen readers can identify the action."},"884":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-37","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#with-dropdown","content":"Wrap a `ToggleButton` in a `MenuTrigger` to add sub-options to a group item."},"885":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-38","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#rtl-direction","content":"The group follows the document's layout direction, detected automatically from the browser locale."},"886":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-39","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#data-attributes","content":"Components automatically add data attributes for styling different states:"},"887":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-40","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#data-attributes","content":"**ToggleButtonGroup Container:** `data-size`"},"888":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-41","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#data-attributes","content":"**ToggleButton Item:** `data-selected`, `data-hovered`, `data-pressed`, `data-focus-visible`, `data-disabled`"},"889":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-42","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#component-customization","content":"Individual components can be styled by passing `className` props:"},"890":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-43","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#keyboard-navigation","content":"Key"},"891