 In / Out / Reset)"},"908":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-61","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#when-to-use","content":"✅ For multi-select scenarios — when users need to select multiple options simultaneously"},"909":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-62","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#when-to-use","content":"❌ For unrelated actions that perform disconnected tasks without shared context"},"910":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-63","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#when-to-use","content":"❌ For more than 5 choices — cognitive overload; consider a **Select** instead"},"911":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-64","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#when-to-use","content":"❌ When actions require strong visual distinction (e.g. Save vs. Delete)"},"912":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-65","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#when-to-use","content":"❌ When selecting an option leads to a different page or workflow — use navigation instead"},"913":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-66","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#when-to-use","content":"❌ For mutually exclusive content views (e.g. Monthly / Yearly) — use **SegmentedController** instead"},"914":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-67","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#keep-variants-consistent","content":"Avoid mixing different content types (text-only, icon-only, icon+text) within the same group. Mixing styles creates visual noise and makes the set feel fragmented rather than unified."},"915":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-68","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#balance-label-lengths","content":"Keep button labels of similar length. Large differences in text length cause irregular button widths and make the group appear uneven. Prefer short, concise wording."},"916":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-69","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#alignment","content":"Align the group to reflect its relationship to surrounding content:"},"917":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-70","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#alignment","content":"**Left** — when the group controls content directly below or within the same column (dashboards, tables)."},"918":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-71","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#alignment","content":"**Center** — when the group acts as a prominent toggle affecting an entire section or page."},"919":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-72","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#alignment","content":"**Right** — when the group represents utility or contextual controls (e.g. grid/list view toggle)."},"920":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-73","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#label-guidelines","content":"Use **title case**: capitalize the first letter of each word, except short prepositions."},"921":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-74","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#label-guidelines","content":"Keep labels to one or two words. Omit articles (a, an, the) and filler words."},"922":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-75","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#label-guidelines","content":"Prefer action-focused or descriptive language that communicates the option instantly."},"923":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-76","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#icon-only-items","content":"Use icon-only items only when the icon's meaning is universally recognized. Always provide an `aria-label` on each icon-only `ToggleButton`:"},"924":{"id":"/docs/components/tooltip","page_id":"/docs/components/tooltip","type":"page","content":"Tooltip","breadcrumbs":["Docs","Components"],"tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/tooltip"},"925":{"id":"/docs/components/tooltip-0","page_id":"/docs/components/tooltip","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/tooltip","content":"The Tooltip component displays a description of an element on hover or focus."},"926":{"id":"/docs/components/tooltip-1","page_id":"/docs/components/tooltip","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/tooltip#installation","content":"Installation"},"927":{"id":"/docs/components/tooltip-2","page_id":"/docs/components/tooltip","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/tooltip#props","content":"Props"},"928":{"id":"/docs/components/tooltip-3","page_id":"/docs/components/tooltip","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/tooltip#examples","content":"Examples"},"929":{"id":"/docs/components/tooltip-4","page_id":"/docs/components/tooltip","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/tooltip#basic-usage","content":"Basic Usage"},"930":{"id":"/docs/components/tooltip-5","page_id":"/docs/components/tooltip","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/tooltip#custom-anchor","content":"Custom Anchor"},"931":{"id":"/docs/components/tooltip-6","page_id":"/docs/components/tooltip","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/tooltip#accessibility","content":"Accessibility"},"932"