ds. For complete API documentation, advanced usage patterns, and implementation details, see the `@bento/icon` and `@bento/svg-parser` package documentation."],[15,"This also works with autocomplete in IDEs and LLMs, so you can import from the root package and let your editor/agent suggest the available components."],[370,"This approach works well for SSR and small numbers of icons, but can lead to DOM bloat when the same icon appears many times."],[715,"Three sizes are available: `sm`, `md` (default), and `lg`."],[632,"Three track heights are available: `xs` (6px), `sm` (12px), and `md` (24px)."],[1224,"Tick labels on both axes with `xLabels` and `yLabels`."],[1225,"Tick marks (short lines) at each tick value. Controlled by `xTickMarks` and `yTickMarks`."],[1184,"Ticks"],[1240,"Time-series with date and currency formatting, gridlines, and nice Y-axis."],[1032,"Title displayed below the x-axis."],[1034,"Title displayed to the left of the y-axis."],[1182,"Titles"],[618,"To position a popover relative to a different element than its trigger, use the\n`triggerRef` and `isOpen` props instead of `<PopoverTrigger>`.\n`onOpenChange` is called when the user opens or closes the popover."],[937,"To position a tooltip relative to a different focusable element, use the\n`triggerRef` prop. The `TooltipTrigger` still handles showing/hiding on hover/focus."],[619,"To show a close button in the popover header, use the `showCloseButton` prop."],[429,"Toggle the drawer via the trigger button"],[897,"Toggle the focused item"],[846,"ToggleButton"],[924,"Tooltip"],[1196,"Tooltip Disabled"],[1217,"Tooltip or Crosshair Not Showing"],[999,"Tooltip Positioning Issues"],[1236,"Tooltip values formatted with `tooltipValueFormatter` (e.g. currency, units)."],[1234,"Tooltip, crosshair, and data point glyphs all disabled (`tooltip={false}`, `showCrosshair={false}`, `showDataPoints={false}`)."],[935,"Tooltips appear after a short delay when hovering, and immediately when the element receives focus